    <div class="container my-5 w-60">
      <p><b>Learning Seeds</b> is the social benefit corporation known for the Enlightened Shadowing Method
        of social coaching for children. Due to the high volume, they currently have an 8-month waitlist
        for their services. In order to help the situation, our design team spent 3 weeks
        working on a micro-course that serves as a funnel to their methods and gives
        parents an opportunity to start learning as soon as possible.</p>
    </div>


    <div class="container w-60 border-style">
      <h3 class="my-3 text-center font-weight-bold">Results</h3>
      <div class="container px-0">
        <p>We designed an educational micro-course that introduces the Enlightened Shadowing Method to novice users
          and teaches how to use it in practice. The course includes the combination of video, infographics,
          audio and text. Users have the ability to save the pieces of information for their future reference as well
          as take notes and track their progress. Each lesson ends with the
          reflection form that allows users to record what tips and practices worked best for their children.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
