        <div class="col-lg-6 px-5">
          <h3 class="my-3 font-weight-bold">Problem statement:</h3>
          <p>Parents need a way to learn enough of the Enlightened Shadowing Method so that
            they will be able to implement aspects of it with their own
            children and experience progress and relief.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 px-5">
          <h3 class="my-3 font-weight-bold">Hypothesis:</h3>
          <p>We believe by creating a micro-course that scales the learnability of the Enlightened Shadow Method, we will enable
            parents to successfully implement these methods as part of their own parenting toolkit.</p>
        </div>

