    <!-------------------Content Research ------------------------->
    <div class="container pb-5 my-5 w-60">
      <h3 class="mb-4 text-center font-weight-bold">Content Research</h3>
    <p>The big part of our research process was familiarizing ourselves with the Enlightened Shadowing Method invented and actively used by Learning Seeds. We also spent some time consulting with the Content Expert who gave us the valuable recommendations on how to better present the method and what is the most important.</p>
    <br> <p>
    As a result, we found out that:</p>
    <br>
    <ul class="pl-3">
      <li><b>“Chunking”</b> the rich content of the method into digestible pieces is key</li>
      <li><b>Mindfulness</b> as a pathway to empathy is highly important</li>
      <li>Parents need to <b>understand the rationale</b> behind the method, then <b>observe and unpack</b> what’s been observed in order to effectively learn Enlightened Shadowing.</li>
      <li><b>Reflection</b> and <b>recording the progress</b> is an integral part of learning the method.</li>
    </ul>
    </div>

